items.sentence: Who told you that Tom was going to Australia?
Everyone thought that Tom was from Australia.
Do you have any idea what we should be doing?
Tom isn't much better at French than Mary is.
He visited me every time he came up to Tokyo.
He is scheduled to come up to Tokyo tomorrow.
I just remembered I have another appointment.
I thought this was just a story for children.
We don't know today what tomorrow will bring.
You can't fit a square peg into a round hole.
